# Error Handling

- AppError: .networkError, .httpError(code:), .decodingError, .authError, .unknown
- ErrorToAppErrorMapper at data boundary
- ViewModel: error: AppError?; clearError() for dismissal
- SwiftUI .alert(isPresented:presenting:) bound to error
- Retryable: NetworkError, 5xx, DecodingError; Fatal: AuthError, 4xx
